OL,3,C'Fast-moving investigation' underway
OL,4,Cafter woman raped in car park
OL,6,FAn investigation is underway after a
OL,7,Fwoman was raped in a car park in
OL,8,FWorthing.
OL,10,FPolice say the incident happened in
OL,11,FLyndhurst Road Car Park shortly after
OL,12,F8pm on Wednesday evening. (11 March)
OL,14,FThe victim, a woman in her 20s, is
OL,15,Fbeing supported by specialist officers
OL,16,Fand the force says a fast-moving
OL,17,Finvestigation is underway.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
