OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773335511
OL,3,C'Fast-moving investigation' underway
OL,4,Cafter woman raped in car park
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Jay Mendis-
OL,7,FGunasekera said: "We are at the early
OL,8,Fstages of this investigation and the
OL,9,Fvictim will continue to receive our
OL,10,Ffull support as this progresses.
OL,12,F"Detectives are exploring a number of
OL,13,Flines of enquiry to identify and
OL,14,Flocate a suspect.
OL,16,F"There will be an increased police
OL,17,Fpresence in the area overnight and
OL,18,Finto the morning, with a closure of
OL,19,Fthe car park expected during the day
OL,20,Fas we gather and preserve any evidence.
